---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="LG Dryer Repair for Property Managers & Landlords | Same Day"
  description="LG dryer repair for property managers in LA, OC, Ventura. Same-day service, remote payment, email reports, 20% below market labor rate."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="pm-hero">
    <div class="pm-label">For property managers & landlords</div>
    <h1>LG Dryer Repair Built for Property Management</h1>
    <p>Same-day service, remote booking, payment on file, and a full service report emailed after every visit. We work around your schedule — not your tenant's.</p>
    <div class="pm-cta-row">
      <a href="tel:3239907550" class="pm-btn-primary">📞 (323) 990-7550</a>
      <a href="#pm-form" class="pm-btn-secondary">Corporate inquiry →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- PAIN POINTS -->
  <div class="pm-pains">
    <div class="pm-pain-card">
      <div class="pm-pain-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1a6cf6" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
          <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Tenant calling at 8am</h3>
      <p>We offer same-day service across LA, Orange County, and Ventura County. In most cases we can be on-site within hours of your call — not days.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pm-pain-card">
      <div class="pm-pain-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1a6cf6" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/>
          <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>You're not on-site</h3>
      <p>Book remotely, leave a payment method on file, and we handle everything with your tenant directly. You get a full service report by email after the visit — no need to be there.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pm-pain-card">
      <div class="pm-pain-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1a6cf6" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/>
          <path d="M3 9h18"/>
          <path d="M9 21V9"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Multiple units to manage</h3>
      <p>Property managers and building managers who work with us regularly receive labor rates 20% below standard market pricing. One point of contact, one invoice per visit, full service history on file.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <div class="pm-how">
    <h2>How it works when you're not on-site</h2>
    <div class="pm-how-steps">

      <div class="pm-how-step">
        <div class="pm-how-num">01</div>
        <h3>You call or fill the form</h3>
        <p>Provide the property address, tenant contact, and a payment method on file. Takes 3 minutes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pm-how-arrow">→</div>

      <div class="pm-how-step">
        <div class="pm-how-num">02</div>
        <h3>We coordinate with the tenant</h3>
        <p>We contact your tenant directly to confirm the 2-hour arrival window. You don't need to be involved.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pm-how-arrow">→</div>

      <div class="pm-how-step">
        <div class="pm-how-num">03</div>
        <h3>Repair completed</h3>
        <p>Technician arrives, diagnoses, and completes the repair. OEM parts only. 85% fixed on the first visit.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pm-how-arrow">→</div>

      <div class="pm-how-step">
        <div class="pm-how-num">04</div>
        <h3>Invoice emailed to you</h3>
        <p>We charge your payment method on file and email a full invoice and service report immediately after the visit via HouseCall Pro.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- WHY US -->
  <div class="pm-why">
    <div class="pm-why-text">
      <h2>Why property managers choose us</h2>
      <p>Managing appliance repairs across multiple units is a headache. A missed appointment, a no-show technician, or an invoice that doesn't match the quote creates more work for you. We built our process to eliminate exactly those problems.</p>
      <p>We service LG dryers exclusively — which means our technicians know every model, every common failure, and carry the right parts on every truck. You're not paying for a generalist who has to look up your unit's service manual on-site.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pm-why-list">
      <div class="pm-why-item">
        <div class="pm-why-check">✓</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pm-why-item-title">Same-day availability</div>
          <div class="pm-why-item-desc">Across LA County, Orange County, and Ventura County</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pm-why-item">
        <div class="pm-why-check">✓</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pm-why-item-title">20% below market labor rate</div>
          <div class="pm-why-item-desc">For property managers and landlords with ongoing service needs</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pm-why-item">
        <div class="pm-why-check">✓</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pm-why-item-title">Payment on file</div>
          <div class="pm-why-item-desc">Card, Zelle, or check — we charge after the job is done</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pm-why-item">
        <div class="pm-why-check">✓</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pm-why-item-title">Invoice & service report by email</div>
          <div class="pm-why-item-desc">Sent automatically via HouseCall Pro after every visit</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pm-why-item">
        <div class="pm-why-check">✓</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pm-why-item-title">3-month warranty on all repairs</div>
          <div class="pm-why-item-desc">1-year warranty on repairs $1,000 and above</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pm-why-item">
        <div class="pm-why-check">✓</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pm-why-item-title">Licensed & insured</div>
          <div class="pm-why-item-desc">Bureau of Household Goods and Services #49573 · BBB A+</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pm-why-item">
        <div class="pm-why-check">✓</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pm-why-item-title">Text notification to tenant</div>
          <div class="pm-why-item-desc">Technician texts 30 minutes before arrival — tenant is never left waiting</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pm-why-item">
        <div class="pm-why-check">✓</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pm-why-item-title">OEM parts only</div>
          <div class="pm-why-item-desc">Genuine LG parts through our supplier network — often below retail price</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CORPORATE INQUIRY FORM -->
  <div class="pm-form-section" id="pm-form">
    <h2>Corporate inquiry</h2>
    <p class="pm-form-sub">Fill out the form and we'll contact you within 2 hours during business hours. Mon–Sat 8am–7pm · Sun 9am–5pm.</p>

    <form class="pm-form" id="propertyManagerForm">
      <div class="pm-form-row">
        <div class="pm-form-group">
          <label for="pm-name">Your name *</label>
          <input type="text" id="pm-name" name="name" placeholder="John Smith" required />
        </div>
        <div class="pm-form-group">
          <label for="pm-company">Company / management company</label>
          <input type="text" id="pm-company" name="company" placeholder="ABC Property Management" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pm-form-row">
        <div class="pm-form-group">
          <label for="pm-phone">Phone *</label>
          <input type="tel" id="pm-phone" name="phone" placeholder="(323) 555-0100" required />
        </div>
        <div class="pm-form-group">
          <label for="pm-email">Email for invoices & reports *</label>
          <input type="email" id="pm-email" name="email" placeholder="manager@company.com" required />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pm-form-group">
        <label for="pm-address">Property address *</label>
        <input type="text" id="pm-address" name="address" placeholder="123 Main St, Los Angeles, CA 90001" required />
      </div>
      <div class="pm-form-row">
        <div class="pm-form-group">
          <label for="pm-units">Number of units at this property</label>
          <input type="number" id="pm-units" name="units" placeholder="e.g. 12" min="1" />
        </div>
        <div class="pm-form-group">
          <label for="pm-tenant">Tenant contact (if known)</label>
          <input type="text" id="pm-tenant" name="tenant" placeholder="Tenant name & phone" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pm-form-group">
        <label for="pm-problem">Describe the problem *</label>
        <textarea id="pm-problem" name="problem" rows="4" placeholder="e.g. LG dryer not heating, model DLGX3901V, unit 4B" required></textarea>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="pm-form-submit">Send inquiry →</button>
      <div class="pm-form-success" id="pmSuccess" style="display:none;">
        ✓ Message received. We'll contact you within 2 hours.
      </div>
      <div class="pm-form-error" id="pmError" style="display:none;">
        Something went wrong. Please call us at (323) 990-7550.
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div class="pm-faq">
    <h2>Common questions from property managers</h2>

    <div class="pm-faq-item">
      <div class="pm-faq-q">Do I need to be present during the repair?</div>
      <div class="pm-faq-a">Not at all. Provide us with the tenant's contact details and a payment method on file when you book. We handle everything with the tenant directly and send you a full service report by email after the visit.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="pm-faq-item">
      <div class="pm-faq-q">How does remote payment work?</div>
      <div class="pm-faq-a">At booking, you provide a card number, Zelle, or arrange check payment. We charge your method on file only after the repair is completed and the tenant has confirmed the unit is working. You receive an itemized invoice immediately via email.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="pm-faq-item">
      <div class="pm-faq-q">What is the 20% labor discount and how do I qualify?</div>
      <div class="pm-faq-a">Property managers, building managers, and landlords who contact us through this page or identify themselves as managing multiple units qualify automatically. The 20% discount applies to the labor portion of every invoice — parts are billed at our standard supplier price which is already typically below retail.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="pm-faq-item">
      <div class="pm-faq-q">Can you service multiple units in the same building on the same day?</div>
      <div class="pm-faq-a">Yes. If you have multiple LG dryers that need service, let us know when you book and we'll schedule them in sequence to minimize travel time and cost.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="pm-faq-item">
      <div class="pm-faq-q">What warranty do you provide on repairs?</div>
      <div class="pm-faq-a">All repairs carry a standard 3-month warranty covering both parts and labor. For repairs of $1,000 and above the warranty extends to 1 full year. If the same issue returns within the warranty period, we return and fix it completely free of charge.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="pm-faq-item">
      <div class="pm-faq-q">Which areas do you cover?</div>
      <div class="pm-faq-a">We cover all of Los Angeles County, Orange County, and Ventura County — including Beverly Hills, Santa Monica, Pasadena, Burbank, Glendale, Long Beach, Torrance, Irvine, Newport Beach, Thousand Oaks, and surrounding cities.</div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- BOTTOM CTA -->
  <div class="pm-bottom-cta">
    <h2>Ready to set up a corporate account?</h2>
    <p>Call us directly or fill out the inquiry form above. We'll have everything set up within one business day.</p>
    <div class="pm-cta-row">
      <a href="tel:3239907550" class="pm-btn-primary">📞 (323) 990-7550</a>
      <a href="#pm-form" class="pm-btn-secondary">Fill out the form →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Do I need to be present during the repair?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Not at all. Provide us with the tenant's contact details and a payment method on file when you book. We handle everything with the tenant directly and send you a full service report by email after the visit."}
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How does remote payment work?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "At booking, you provide a card number, Zelle, or arrange check payment. We charge your method on file only after the repair is completed and the tenant has confirmed the unit is working. You receive an itemized invoice immediately via email."}
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What is the 20% labor discount and how do I qualify?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Property managers, building managers, and landlords who contact us through this page or identify themselves as managing multiple units qualify automatically. The 20% discount applies to the labor portion of every invoice — parts are billed at our standard supplier price which is already typically below retail."}
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can you service multiple units in the same building on the same day?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. If you have multiple LG dryers that need service, let us know when you book and we'll schedule them in sequence to minimize travel time and cost."}
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What warranty do you provide on repairs?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "All repairs carry a standard 3-month warranty covering both parts and labor. For repairs of $1,000 and above the warranty extends to 1 full year. If the same issue returns within the warranty period, we return and fix it completely free of charge."}
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Which areas do you cover?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "We cover all of Los Angeles County, Orange County, and Ventura County — including Beverly Hills, Santa Monica, Pasadena, Burbank, Glendale, Long Beach, Torrance, Irvine, Newport Beach, Thousand Oaks, and surrounding cities."}
      }
    ]
  })} />

</Layout>

<script is:inline>
  document.getElementById('propertyManagerForm').addEventListener('submit', async function(e) {
    e.preventDefault();
    const btn = this.querySelector('.pm-form-submit');
    btn.textContent = 'Sending...';
    btn.disabled = true;

    const name = document.getElementById('pm-name').value;
    const company = document.getElementById('pm-company').value;
    const phone = document.getElementById('pm-phone').value;
    const email = document.getElementById('pm-email').value;
    const address = document.getElementById('pm-address').value;
    const units = document.getElementById('pm-units').value;
    const tenant = document.getElementById('pm-tenant').value;
    const problem = document.getElementById('pm-problem').value;

    const message = `[CORPORATE CLIENT]
Name: ${name}
Company: ${company || 'not specified'}
Phone: ${phone}
Email: ${email}
Address: ${address}
Units in building: ${units || 'not specified'}
Tenant contact: ${tenant || 'not specified'}
Problem: ${problem}`;

    try {
      const response = await fetch('/api/contact', {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
        body: JSON.stringify({ name, phone, email, message })
      });
      if (response.ok) {
        document.getElementById('pmSuccess').style.display = 'block';
        this.reset();
      } else {
        document.getElementById('pmError').style.display = 'block';
      }
    } catch {
      document.getElementById('pmError').style.display = 'block';
    } finally {
      btn.textContent = 'Send inquiry →';
      btn.disabled = false;
    }
  });
</script>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .pm-hero { max-width: 760px; margin: 60px auto 80px; text-align: center; padding: 0 24px; }
  .pm-label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #1a6cf6; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .pm-hero h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.2; }
  .pm-hero p { font-size: 1.05rem; color: #c8d0dc; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .pm-cta-row { display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .pm-btn-primary { background: #1a6cf6; color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
  .pm-btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: #1a6cf6; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; border: 1px solid #1a6cf6; }

  /* Pain cards */
  .pm-pains { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto 80px; padding: 0 24px; }
  .pm-pain-card { background: #111111; border: 1px solid #1e2a3a; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px 24px; }
  .pm-pain-icon { width: 44px; height: 44px; background: rgba(26,108,246,0.1); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .pm-pain-icon svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; }
  .pm-pain-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .pm-pain-card p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #c8d0dc; line-height: 1.75; }

  /* How it works */
  .pm-how { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto 80px; padding: 0 24px; }
  .pm-how h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .pm-how-steps { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px; }
  .pm-how-step { flex: 1; background: #111111; border: 1px solid #1e2a3a; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px 20px; }
  .pm-how-num { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #1a6cf6; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .pm-how-step h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .pm-how-step p { font-size: 0.83rem; color: #c8d0dc; line-height: 1.7; }
  .pm-how-arrow { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #1a6cf6; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 48px; opacity: 0.5; }

  /* Why section */
  .pm-why { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 64px; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto 80px; padding: 0 24px; align-items: start; }
  .pm-why-text h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .pm-why-text p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #c8d0dc; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .pm-why-item { display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .pm-why-check { width: 22px; height: 22px; background: rgba(26,108,246,0.12); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.75rem; color: #1a6cf6; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
  .pm-why-item-title { font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 600; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .pm-why-item-desc { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #8a9ab0; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* Form */
  .pm-form-section { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto 80px; padding: 0 24px; }
  .pm-form-section h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .pm-form-sub { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #8a9ab0; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .pm-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
  .pm-form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
  .pm-form-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .pm-form-group label { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #8a9ab0; font-weight: 500; }
  .pm-form-group input,
  .pm-form-group textarea { background: #111111; border: 1px solid #1e2a3a; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 14px; color: #ffffff; font-size: 0.9rem; outline: none; resize: vertical; font-family: inherit; }
  .pm-form-group input:focus,
  .pm-form-group textarea:focus { border-color: #1a6cf6; }
  .pm-form-group input::placeholder,
  .pm-form-group textarea::placeholder { color: #555; }
  .pm-form-submit { background: #1a6cf6; color: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; align-self: flex-start; font-family: inherit; }
  .pm-form-submit:hover { background: #1558d0; }
  .pm-form-submit:disabled { opacity: 0.6; cursor: not-allowed; }
  .pm-form-success { background: rgba(26,108,246,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(26,108,246,0.3); border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 18px; color: #1a6cf6; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .pm-form-error { background: rgba(220,50,50,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(220,50,50,0.3); border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 18px; color: #ff6b6b; font-size: 0.9rem; }

  /* FAQ */
  .pm-faq { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto 80px; padding: 0 24px; }
  .pm-faq h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .pm-faq-item { border-top: 1px solid #1e2a3a; padding: 24px 0; }
  .pm-faq-item:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid #1e2a3a; }
  .pm-faq-q { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .pm-faq-a { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #c8d0dc; line-height: 1.75; }

  /* Bottom CTA */
  .pm-bottom-cta { text-align: center; padding: 60px 24px 80px; border-top: 1px solid #1e2a3a; max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .pm-bottom-cta h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .pm-bottom-cta p { color: #8a9ab0; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 32px; line-height: 1.7; }

  /* Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pm-hero h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; }
    .pm-pains { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .pm-how-steps { flex-direction: column; }
    .pm-how-arrow { display: none; }
    .pm-why { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .pm-form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .pm-form-submit { width: 100%; }
  }
</style>
